data.description: Beautiful 3-bedroom 2 bath home located in North Tucson! Great open floor plan with new wood vinyl plank throughout, a large living room leading to the kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, and a breakfast bar. The backyard includes a storage shed, mountain views and no backyard neighbors! NEW ROOF in 2021 and equipped with solar that helps with year-round energy savings. This home is just minutes to grocery stores, coffee shops and more!
